      "role": "user",
      "content": "can u elaborate on those trends though? like when you say some groups have higher rates, is the literature suggesting there's any inherent link between those specific ethnicities and certain types of criminal behavior, or is it strictly about the policing and systemic stuff u mentioned? just trying to see if there's any consensus on the \"why\" behind the stats.",
